jumpingjacks.title: Jumping Jacks
jumpingjacks.description: If you are able to, do 30 seconds of jumping jacks. Common alternatives may include marching in place or doing a brisk walk. The point is to get your heart rate up and blood flowing through your body.

pushups.title: Push-Ups
pushups.description: If you are able to, do 15 Push-Ups. Common alternatives may include Knee Push-Ups or Inclined Push-Ups. Just make sure your heart starts beating a bit faster and you feel your muscle engorging to some degree.
